&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure class=&#39;gallery-item&#39;&gt; &#xA;  &lt;div class=&#39;gallery-icon landscape&#39;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;img width=&#34;150&#34; height=&#34;150&#34; src=&#34;https://mikedixson.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/14483692234_66a29b3c0c_z-150x150.jpg&#34; class=&#34;attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; /&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I recently took part in a 24 hour photo shoot event whereby the participants were directed and could wander around London and throughout the day were text messaged little missions.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;It was great phone and that, coupled with turning a corner with my processing of photos I have produced some of the most professional photos I have ever made.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I hope you enjoy them. Please go and check out the rest (of which there are many) on my &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.flickr.com/photos/mikedixson/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;flickr page.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;</description>
